name: Rectangular Hand Stamped Sterling Silver Pendant with birthstones
description:
Hand Stamped Sterling Silver Tag with birthstones and a Sterling Silver Necklace comes to you gift wrapped. 


Charms are hand stamped using individual letter stamping tools, therefore no two are exactly alike. Letters and numbers may not be perfectly straight or aligned properly, and spacing may vary. This adds to the charm of your 
custom piece and should not be seen as a defect, but as a one of a kind item.

name: Names with Birthstones - Round Sterling Silver Disc and Necklace - Hand Stamped and Personalized
description:
A 3/4 in. (19mm) sterling silver disc is stamped with the names of your choice.  Birthstone crystals complete this piece.

A beautiful sterling silver chain with lobster clasp closure is included with your purchase. The chain is 18 inches – it can be shortened or lengthened (up to 20 inches) upon request.

Please include personalization information in Message to Seller box at checkout.

*Additional silver charms can be added to this necklace for $4 each. If you need more charms, please contact me for a custom listing.

Please note: This is a handmade item. All stamping is done entirely by hand. Variations in letter placement and spacing will occur. Everything won’t always be straight and perfect – this is the charm of hand-stamping. These variations add to the unique beauty of your handcrafted piece.

name: Silver Heart Dog Tag- Personalized Hand Stamped Charm/Pendant
description:
This charm/pendant is silver plated and has an open heart in the center. It can be hand stamped with two names of your choice. 

Crystals can be added for an additional $4.00 per crystal. 

Charms are hand stamped using individual letter stamping tools, therefore no two are exactly alike. Letters and numbers may not be perfectly straight or aligned properly, and spacing may vary. This adds to the charm of your 
custom piece and should not be seen as a defect, but as a one of a kind item.

Please note that the photo in the listing is a representation of the necklace you will recieve. ** Please leave me a message upon checkout with the names you would like.

name: Vintaj Nickle Free Square Brass Charm - Customized with birthstones
description:
Vintaj has artfully designed their brass jewelry to achieve a weatherworn appearance, emulating dramatic aging through unique conditions. The appearance of each piece is unique and may not be uniform. 

Handstamped items are made by hand and each letter is stamped one-by-one. Lettering and spacing won't be perfectly even, but that just adds to the charm of a handmade piece. 

**Please leave your personalization info and color birthstone upon check out
